Description: TUI client for Geph 5 (MikuClub)
 A lightweight terminal user interface client for the Geph 5 VPN service.
 Provides SOCKS5/HTTP proxy and TUN VPN modes with an interactive TUI.
 .
 Daemon management via the bundled mikuctl command:
   mikuctl start|stop|restart|status|log
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.17)
